Spin up a standalone pulp instance

Pre-reqs
--------

* Make sure your your distros base channel is enabled (rhel-7-server-rpms on RHEL7, base on CentOS7)
* Make sure the hostname is resolveable
* Internet access

Installation
------------

# git clone https://github.com/opuk/pulp-standalone.git
# cd pulp-standalone
# ./runme.sh

Troubleshooting
---------------

1. Poke hole in the firewall as needed.
